<div class="p-3 rounded mb-3" style="background:var(--pm-info-soft);font-size:13px"><i class="bi bi-shield-check me-1"></i> You will be redirected to the bank's secure portal
                            to authorise read + transfer access. PayMo will never see your banking credentials.</div>
<div class="form-check mb-2"><input checked="" class="form-check-input" type="checkbox"/><label class="form-check-label" style="font-size:13px">Allow view balance &amp;
                                transactions</label></div>
<div class="form-check mb-2"><input checked="" class="form-check-input" type="checkbox"/><label class="form-check-label" style="font-size:13px">Allow instant transfers
