                        closed with minimal operational impact, saving KES 18,200 annually in fees.</p>
</div>
<div class="modal-footer"><button (click)="closeModal('optimizeModal2')" class="btn-pm" data-bs-dismiss="modal" type="button">Close</button><button (click)="processAction('optimizeModal2', 'Optimisation plan saved.', '')" class="btn-pm btn-pm-p" type="button">Adopt
                        Plan</button></div>
</div>
</div>
</div><div (click)="closeModal('testModal')" [attr.aria-hidden]="isModalOpen('testModal') ? null : 'true'" [attr.aria-modal]="isModalOpen('testModal') ? 'true' : null" [class.show]="isModalOpen('testModal')" [style.display]="isModalOpen('testModal') ? 'block' : 'none'" class="modal fade R" id="testModal" tabindex="-1">
<div (click)="$event.stopPropagation()" class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
<div class="modal-content">
<div class="modal-header">
<h5 class="modal-title"><i class="bi bi-eye me-2"></i>Test Modal</h5><button (click)="closeModal('testModal')" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" type="button"></button>
</div>
